status: MARC21-007: Base of emulsion of projected resource
Type of material for the base of the emulsion of a photonegative, filmstrip, slide, or transparency.

preferred label (en): film base, other than safety film

definition (en): Material varies for different items in a collection.
scope note (en): Typically this would be used for groups of projected graphics on various bases.

definition (en): Base of emulsion other than glass, synthetic, safety film, film base, other than safety film, mixed collection, paper.
